title: Fixed application crash when it goes to background.
message:
Fixed application crash when it goes to background.
Problem that in order to have abstract square within which points should be displayed we are calculating it when application gets notification from GoogleAPI that it is connected.
And when application goes to background this message is sent but currentuPosition for the user is null at that time. So the fix was to verify either currentPosition is null and if not only then calculate abstract square.
